flowRoot.flowPara: This is part of a model of the solar system.
Mars orbits the sun in about two of our years,
which means this goes around Lake Eola fountain
in a rough circle, at half the pace of a snail.
At the scale of this model (1:44 million),
light travels as fast as a quick jog.
